{"tid":534996,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【趣blogblog】李小加三億all in港交所 你跟唔跟！（股榮）","createTime":"2018-01-20T11:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T16:28:41.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b96d8aff4098d568161ca7b8d9e14ec9a38348c","tid":534996,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"過去幾日，收到很多戰友問，港交所（388）現價可以買嗎？在此一併解答。<br />\n<br />\n記得由去年初已叫網友分注入，有人半信半疑，有人寧揀更好選擇，對我而言，由平均價220元坐落的貨底，就算到了今日達到初步目標$300，亦一股未沽。<br />\n如果去年港股主角是騰訊(700)，今年就是港交所(388)。騰訊去年升一倍，港交所今年在北水帶旺成交、H股全流通憧憬、同股不同權即將實現下，何解不能重演騰訊去年的絕技。很多人以為我講388中線目標$388是開玩笑，但好認真講，$388只是時間問題，快則上半年達標，也不會驚訝。<br />\n對港交所最有信心的人，心目中只有一個，就是行政總裁(CEO)李小加。自2010年正式上任CEO，李小加每年除穩定獲取約二千萬元董事酬金，過去四個年度，每年亦獲取約二千萬元以股份支付酬金。自2010年開始，李小加每年平均獲取逾十萬股港交所股份。而最重要是，到去年底止，他一股也沒有沽，累積股份數目接近100萬股，以上周四收市價297.6元計，市值接近3億元。<br />\n如果是家族生意，CEO只揸不沽可以理解，但作為一個私營機構，李小加CEO身份其實只是打工性質，沽出股份袋袋平安，反而是很合理的動作，八年間只儲不沽，我諗來諗去，只有一個原因，不是公司給你信心，而是國家給你任務，而這個任務一旦完成，就是十倍歸還的時刻。<br />\n沒錯，中港由滬港通、深港通、債券通相繼互聯互通，繼而計劃中的ETF通、同股不同權、H股全流通，以至在港推A股期貨及衍生工具，中港兩地平台整合的藍圖，其實已經由李小加「劇透」了。北水湧港，是大勢所趨，港股的話語權，亦漸由中資主導。<br />\n絕對的信心，建基於背後有最高的指示。三億all in港交所，對沒成本的李小加而言，有贏冇輸。至於大家信不信，反正我信了。<br />\n股榮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstockwing1&d=asHCf3I7mV5Ffg3ruDbINwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=77d047c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stockwing1</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516438901_7bc3.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180120%2Flarge%2F1516438901_7bc3.jpg&d=asHCf3I7mV5Ffg3ruDbINwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=b275dc2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180120/large/1516438901_7bc3.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180120/57729185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57729185&d=asHCf3I7mV5Ffg3ruDbINwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=04ac6089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180120%2F57729185&h=ce08b371\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180120/57729185</a>"},{"pid":"8f0cb13551f5fe11b112c5b5a10fcfb85a5bf855","tid":534996,"uid":22757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T12:58:55.000Z","msg":"冇錢入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d641c189df46168d0e20d814b2b1a4a90f80ab8","tid":534996,"uid":5419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"Ceo持股好正常，無咩特別"},{"pid":"1d1ec67d7067c6810bcf93c957d6ca20c2af3ae7","tid":534996,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"香港人D錢就咁入左條共狗李小加度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港股老千當道：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61065fa0df6cfa89285fcce5f36d82f9342deef8","tid":534996,"uid":70497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1ec67d7067c6810bcf93c957d6ca20c2af3ae7","tid":534996,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"香港人D錢就咁入左條共狗李小加度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港股老千當道：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T14:37:19.000Z","msg":"條友咁廢點解可以做咁多年？"},{"pid":"81b7c214f9aef8c7cf155d2b23782f657e49e9f4","tid":534996,"uid":56999,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"61065fa0df6cfa89285fcce5f36d82f9342deef8","tid":534996,"uid":70497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1ec67d7067c6810bcf93c957d6ca20c2af3ae7","tid":534996,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco